Algorithm (Step-by-Step)StartDisplay main menu with options: Register, Login, ExitGet user choiceIf choice is Register:Prompt for username and passwordCheck if username already existsIf no, create new user and saveReturn to main menuIf choice is Login:Prompt for username and passwordVerify credentialsIf valid, display logged-in menu with options: Add Study Session, View Report, LogoutIn logged-in menu:If Add Study Session: Input subject, date, duration, break; add sessionIf View Report: Calculate total study time and per subject time; display to userIf Logout: Return to main menuIf choice is Exit: Terminate programRepeat until exit
